# Skill Engine (Phase 16)

Read **[SKILL_ENGINE.md](../../SKILL_ENGINE.md)**. **Every future capability must be a skill** registered in `lib/core/skills/registry.ts`.

## Before implementing a skill

1. Define full `SkillDefinition` metadata (`lib/core/skills/types.ts`)
2. Choose category: operational · customer · executive · installation · companion · future
3. Determine layer per [CORE_FOUNDATION.md §21](../../CORE_FOUNDATION.md#21-skill-placement-rules)
4. Add to `SKILL_REGISTRY` — no shipping without registry entry
5. Follow release pipeline: internal → Unonight → limited → GA

> Features create software. Skills create intelligence.
